"03:59.760 It's really good.  03:59.760 --> 04:00.760 Yeah.  04:00.760 --> "
"04:02.760 All right.  04:02.760 --> 04:11.960 So, but for this day, we will "
"also talk about the digital decade policy program, which 04:11.960 --> "
"04:19.200 wants to set up a monitoring and cooperation mechanism to achieve "
"the common objectives 04:19.200 --> 04:23.200 and targets for Europe's "
