"WEBVTT 00:00.000 --> 00:06.000 Dear listener, before we start with the "
"Software Freedom Podcast, we have a very short announcement.  00:06.000 --> "
"00:13.000 Over the past months, the FSFE's online payment provider has "
"repeatedly requested access 00:13.000 --> 00:18.000 to the private data of "
"our supporters, which we obviously refuse.  00:18.000 --> 00:21.000 As a "
"result, our contract was terminated.  00:21.000 --> 00:26.000 And during the "
"migration to a new provider, we may lose some supporters.  00:26.000 --> "
"00:30.000 To continue our work for Free Software, we need your support.  "
"00:30.000 --> 00:37.000 If you are already a supporter, please check your "
"inbox for more information.  00:37.000 --> 00:44.000 If you are not a "
"supporter, you can contribute financially at FSFE.org 00:44.000 --> "
"00:47.000 slash donate and help us over the next months.  00:47.000 --> "
"00:50.000 Thank you very much for listening to the Software Freedom Podcast "
"00:50.000 --> 00:53.000 and supporting the Free Software Foundation Europe.  "
"00:57.000 --> 01:02.000 And I think this is still one of the biggest "
